{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Welcome to VIA </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a medieval fantasy world full of strategic PvP battles without the need for grinding. In VIA Online, you choose your path as a Merchant, Guardian, or Thief\u2014your success depends on your gear, decisions and skills!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Core Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Combat-Heading.png?t=1731253225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Show your mastery of real-time combat in intense encounters where reflexes and tactics matter just as much as your character's strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Combat.gif?t=1731253225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Classes-Heading.png?t=1731253225\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Knight</strong><br>Wield a massive two-handed sword and dominate in close combat with unparalleled defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Knight.gif?t=1731253225\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wizard</strong><br>Manipulate arcane powers, unleashing devastating area-of-effect spells and magical shields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Wizzard.gif?t=1731253225\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Archer</strong><br>Utilize precision strikes and nature's powers to take down enemies from a distance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Archer-Coming-Soon.png?t=1731253225\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Caravan-Heading.png?t=1731253225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the heart of VIA is the Caravan System, where merchants transport valuable goods between towns. Thieves lie in wait to steal them, while Guardians protect the caravans. This balanced system offers high-stakes PvP where strategy and risk management are key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Caravan.gif?t=1731253225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Crafting-Heading.png?t=1731253225\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources from the open world, hunt down rare monsters, and craft powerful items to help you in battle. With a rich crafting system, your progress feels meaningful as you grow stronger. Say goodbye to endless leveling. Instead, focus on improving your gear and upgrading your professions to increase your power and influence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/VIA-Online-Openworld-Heading.png?t=1731253225\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in epic encounters with legendary monsters, explore a vast open world, and discover hidden treasures in dangerous dungeons. Play solo or with friends, taking on group content or challenging PvP battles.</p>","background":"https